Instructions for using the calculator:
1.Dial any number you need!
2.Put a math symbol(There is a choice:addition, subtraction, multiplication, division)
3.Dial the second number you choose!
4.Click on equal.
The output will be the number that was obtained using the mathematical operation you chose,if you need to recalculate something, then press the “С” button and follow the instructions.
Please do not judge my program by its full rigor, this is my first project in java, it turned out quite well, a very simple calculator that each of you can write and understand the code very easily. I am open to your suggestions to make the code simpler and more practical.
